name: enrich
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "enrich" %}
{% set version = "1.2.7" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/enrich-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0a2ab0d2931dff8947012602d1234d2a3ee002d9a355b5d70be6bf5466008893

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools_scm >=1.15.0
    - setuptools_scm_git_archive >=1.0
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - rich >=9.5.1

test:
  imports:
    - enrich
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/pycontribs/enrich
  summary: enrich
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
